+// Span-at-consumption for [Span Backgrounds]: called from every hooked reader of the
+// constraint width ([reg+0x1BC]). Full-screen elements (title/menu/pause backgrounds)
+// never pass the UI-Constraints or size-setter sites, so the only universal interception
